---
title: Vegetarian Sweet Chili Bowls with Protein Shreds and Ginger Rice
description: This is a rice bowl for all to love! It's jam-packed with flavour and hits all the notes that a classic Asian-inspired veggie bowl is known and loved for. A bed of fluffy ginger rice catches all the goodness. Tonight's dinner is sure to leave no plate uncleaned!
